<p><a name="Deep_structure_and_surface_structure" id="Deep_structure_and_surface_structure"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Transformational_grammar&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1" title="Edit section: Deep structure and surface structure">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Deep structure and surface structure</span></h2>
